rows.label: qst105606_msg001
rows.name: 目的は達成できた

rows.label: qst105606_msg0001
rows.name: That's the last of them!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0002
rows.name: Your Highness! Glad to see you're safe!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0003
rows.name:
We've got the insurgents
under control here.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0004
rows.name:
Damn it! You're the ones who
need to be punished, not us!
You lied to us! To your people!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0005
rows.name:
Don't you care for your country?
You have no blood ties with
Adel, you realize that?!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0006
rows.name:
After hundreds of years of
deception, now is the time to
take down your sham of a family, and-

rows.label: qst105606_msg0007
rows.name:
That's enough. I don't want to
have to resort to undue force.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0008
rows.name: Hah! The prodigal son has spoken!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0009
rows.name:
We're the victims here! Have you ever
stopped to look at your people?

rows.label: qst105606_msg0010
rows.name:
People are starving, freezing to
death! All because we're being
governed by a false monarch!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0011
rows.name: I said shut your damn mouth!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0012
rows.name:
I know what you're trying to say. I
feel cheated just as much as you.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0013
rows.name:
But I fail to see how the state of
the capital's got anything to do with
whether my dad's got Adel's blood!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0014
rows.name:
You can judge us however you
like. Just wait until we've got
Luxuria back on its feet first.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0015
rows.name: Your Highness...

rows.label: qst105606_msg0016
rows.name:
Hah! Your opinion is duly
noted, "Your Highness".

rows.label: qst105606_msg0017
rows.name:
We've done our part. It
won't be long now...

rows.label: qst105606_msg0018
rows.name:
Soon, the royal family will fall
at the hands of Adel himself!
Aha...ahaha...AAAHAHAHAHA!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0019
rows.name:
Adel himself? What's
that supposed to mean?

rows.label: qst105606_msg0020
rows.name:
You'll just have to wait and
see, won't you? HA-hahahaha!!!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0021
rows.name:
This isn't going anywhere. You there.
Take care of this chap, will you? Wring
everything you can out of him.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0022
rows.name: Your Highness! Leave it to me!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0023
rows.name:
Just remember, he used to be
on our side. Go easy on him.

rows.label: qst105606_msg0024
rows.name: Yes, Your Highness!

rows.label: qst105606_msg0025
rows.name: My Prince, the key...

rows.label: qst105606_msg0026
rows.name:
Right, yeah, I'm on it. But ugh,
talk about a weird threat. I just
hope it doesn't amount to more...
